experiments.name: DenseNet121_Chexpert_BCE_E5_B32_C0_N12_D256_DS9010_LR4
experiments.description:
Trained DenseNet121 architecture using the 'Chexpert_BCE_E5_B32_C0_N12_D256_DS9010_LR4' benchmark. The benchmark was initialized for the chexpert_full dataset with batch size of 32, shuffle set to True and images rescaled to dimension (256, 256).
The training was done for 5 epochs using the Adam optimizer and binary_crossentropy loss.
A total of 12 labels/pathologies were included in the training and encoded using the 'uzeroes' method.
The traing set included 200278 number of sample, the validation set 234, and the test set 234.
